messageSegments.text: From working on this a few times now it's usually custom fields on standard objects in the Data Sync (in Einstein Analytics Studio under Data Manager and Connect > SFDC_LOCAL).
If you check the package components on the installed package and look at Custom Fields and what objects they are on it usually gives clues what to look for.
